text: The movie Diana is a 2013 British-French-Belgian-Swedish biographical movie. It is on the life of Princess Diana. In particular, the movie is about the last two years of her life after her divorce from Prince Charles. Naomi Watts plays Diana. The movie was released on 20 September 2013 in the UK. It was condemned almost immediately by British press.
